All data collected by the ATLAS detector undergo careful scrutiny to ensure the quality of the recorded information; data used for the efficiency measurements are filtered by requiring that all detector subsystems needed in the analysis (calorimeters and tracking detectors) are operating nominally. After all data-quality requirements (94% efficient), 37.1  fb-1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
