The lower efficiencies of the Medium and Tight operating points compared to Loose result in an increased rejection of background; the rejection factors for misidentified electrons from multijet production (evaluated with the two-to-two process simulation sample described in Sect. 3) increase typically by factors of approximately 2.5 for Medium and 5 for Tight compared to Loose, in the ET\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
