				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\eta $$\end{document}, as shown by comparing the equivalent two distributions in Fig. 13 (top, left).

